dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.body:
Attention Google: 

Further to our previous Urgent Notices of Copyright Infringement, I am writing on behalf of Zuffa, LLC and/or its subsidiaries and affiliated companies, to notify you of the continued infringement of Zuffa, LLC's intellectual property rights in the titles identified in this email in Google search results.  Notices of Copyright Infringement were previously sent to Google for the identified titles and links on the dates listed in this email.

Zuffa, LLC repeats our demand that Google take immediate action to stop such infringements.

The search results and links identified in this email are specific examples of Google search results linking to logos, images, artwork, video files, video streams and websites that infringe upon Zuffa, LLC's intellectual property rights.

Zuffa, LLC hereby repeats its demand that Google promptly remove and disable the links to all unauthorized copies of works whose copyrights are owned by Zuffa, LLC of which it is aware, including the infringing files identified in this email. 

This letter is not a complete statement of Zuffa, LLC's rights in connection with this matter, and nothing contained herein constitutes an express or implied waiver of any rights, remedies, or defenses of Zuffa, LLC in connection with this matter, all of which are expressly reserved. 

The undersigned has a good faith belief that use of the materials in the manner described herein is not authorized by Zuffa, LLC, its agent, or the law. The information in this notice is accurate. Under penalty of perjury, the undersigned is authorized to act on behalf of Zuffa, LLC with respect to this matter.

IMPORTANT NOTICE:  None of the information contained in this legal notice is to be transmitted and/or released to any third party, including but not limited to Chilling Effects (chillingeffects.org), without the express written permission of the the copyright owner and or his agent.  As stated in Section 512 of the Digital Millennium Copyright Act, and in the normal course of processing and notifying the infringing counter party, recipient must only include information specific to that counter party's infringement and must not include this entire notice. Any re-transmission in whole or in part of this legal notice by the intended recipient will be a direct violation of U.S. and International Copyright Law and will be prosecuted to the fullest extent of the law by the copyright owner. 

Please also note that with the express permission of the copyright owner, in addition to being forwarded to certain members of the United States Congress and the U.S. Department of Justice, MiMTiD will send this legal notice to a third-party that aggregates repeat infringer data gathered by different agencies and infringement mitigation service companies around the globe and provides centralized access to that data to be used by global policy makers and law enforcement agencies to create and enforce copyright law. As such, this legal notice will be included in The Chilling Report (http://www.chillingreport.com). To obtain secure access to the Chilling Report please email The Chilling Report at [redacted]chillingreport.com or call [redacted].

We appreciate your prompt attention to this important matter.

Sincerely,
MiMTiD Corp.
[redacted]
Managing Director
[redacted]
[redacted]mimtid.com
